## Execution Strategy

```
B1 → B2 → B3 (concurrency cleanup, one session)
C1 → C2 → C3 → C4 (database refactor, multiple sessions)
C5 → C6 → C7 → C8 (protocols & services, multiple sessions)
```

## Rollback Notes

Each phase is independent. If a phase causes regressions:
1. Revert the specific commits
2. Add missing characterization tests
3. Re-attempt with narrower scope
